[Laboratory confirmation of the EV-71 case in Thailand is awaited. The case in the Philippines indicates that EV-71 infection is wide-spread in South-east Asia and China at the present time, and that the signs and symptoms of EV-71 infection may not always be either severe or even characteristic of HFMD.

Davao City is the administrative centre of Davao Region and can be located in the interactive HealthMap at:
